{"tid":1429660,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"萬萬不可以屌鳩人影相","createTime":"2019-08-07T14:22:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T15:00:53.000Z","uid":121961,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d154ba7a2dff0f01113fc3ef14bb096d1a6ca390","tid":1429660,"uid":121961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T14:22:28.000Z","msg":"我理得你放火燒差館<br />\n總之唔可以屌鳩街坊影相<br />\n一班街坊都係花生友八掛睇發生咩事<br />\n而家我地屌鳩佢地  <br />\n佢地會驚左我地  <br />\n咁仲有邊個撐我地？<br />\n佢地影相嘅時候  <br />\n我地可以有啲禮貌講「唔該唔好影相呀  唔好影大頭  我地被黑警認到會好麻煩架」 <br />\n佢地可能會為你著想唔再影<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲有我地打黑社會  <br />\n班街坊會驚  <br />\n因為佢地成世人都未見過群毆  <br />\n會驚刀槍無眼 殃及無辜  <br />\n只要我地打黑社會嘅時候講「打街坊呀喇  警察唔保護街坊  唯有我地保護街坊」  <br />\n街坊就會知對象唔係佢地 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">香港加油</span>"},{"pid":"5a81f9142eee569b7c3c66e61b8a42f120a5a534","tid":1429660,"uid":121961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T14:38:55.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"b7441c7266566dbb0c714ae8e8abf2a7008d9c55","tid":1429660,"uid":121961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T14:39:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8511db88023b789f5422333463136701c305924","tid":1429660,"uid":121961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T14:39:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd1abce1293200b4b0cb68791b322c2c59dad5c4","tid":1429660,"uid":121961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T14:39:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da13106a16271fa1a5322b51d3fd6af0d9832ab8","tid":1429660,"uid":6363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T14:40:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cff91e632d825e0b6b1813dcc9525d4d4008cd73","tid":1429660,"uid":291962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T14:42:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"26c4db92cdc8226052febdd7bc9a4754ba7d63c4","tid":1429660,"uid":272812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T14:43:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d124ce87d00ede18f3ea29229e799091406df66","tid":1429660,"uid":262093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T14:43:56.000Z","msg":"「呢拳係幫街坊打嘅」<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好有電影feel。"},{"pid":"f1f240790fd45ba4a193800bd4d3a761c3c066ac","tid":1429660,"uid":268643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T14:45:14.000Z","msg":"發夢冷靜派同我入嚟<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1427811\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1427811</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1081349fa106e6289badff3cc1fdf1afdde5167c","tid":1429660,"uid":168214,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T14:57:37.000Z","msg":"大家有懷疑就問下佢<br />\n我相信除左藍屍 態度都應該好好<br />\n甚至係請佢俾你睇下影咩相<br />\n唔俾就可以用你身軀遮住鏡頭<br />\n錄返佢片 然後警告 <br />\n最後搶手機<br />\n<br />\n一定要錄片<br />\n一黎唔俾對方玩野<br />\n二黎同自己手足有收斂作用"},{"pid":"49688f57bc548a47cd51e3115a974943d3c69f01","tid":1429660,"uid":212274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T15:00:53.000Z","msg":"成日話唔好影相，其實記者行到咁近直播咩都影曬，所以叫人唔好影相係好無謂，落場做足裝保護措施先重要"}]}